sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Host
    participant GE as game_engine
    actor PL as Players

    H->>GE: start msg
    GE->>H: question msg (includes scoring_rule)
    GE->>PL: question msg (BroadcastAll, includes scoring_rule)
    Note over GE: countdown timer
    PL->>GE: answer msg
    GE->>GE: session.scoring_rule.calculate_points()
    GE->>PL: feedback (PlayerOnly)
    GE->>H: question_result (HostOnly)
    GE->>H: leaderboard (BroadcastAll)
    GE->>PL: leaderboard (BroadcastAll)
